{"tid":109891,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[學神]轉彎問題求救","createTime":"2017-02-06T09:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T07:55:16.000Z","uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f426096ae514eaddf9a52e6a91616094fac63454","tid":109891,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:53:34.000Z","msg":"兜左兩堂圈 轉極都領略唔到轉彎技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一時扭太多 一時扭轉少 有次仲唔小心上左少少壆 好彩條路無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉極都轉唔好 師傅屌撚到我上天花板 又鬧我蠢撚過豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86807af796659be8f499052a52684cc2ea6590c7","tid":109891,"uid":9794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"1212"},{"pid":"01ab013d9e440de12431d3e31c28ecd8bf052712","tid":109891,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"屌，落機鋪玩兩轉灣岸頭D 先啦，呢啲嘢講感覺㗎嘛"},{"pid":"c52dee3a7cdeecc51d78178610f2f7caf83cc2c6","tid":109891,"uid":9794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:56:50.000Z","msg":"你每次入彎都攞唔到最佳嘅路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68aae91da586d36744c4619dae26dc1c6fcd034","tid":109891,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，落機鋪玩兩轉灣岸頭D 先啦，呢啲嘢講感覺㗎嘛</blockquote><br />\n係咪認真有用先？<br />\n係嘅話我聽晚即刻去揸兩揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利伸小弟真心撚 但求巴打唔好老點我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60229d09a41caf7595ddf761802ad89aadcb8cde","tid":109891,"uid":31796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"轉緊嗰陣可以調節堂軚唔好定死一個位<br />\n你見到開始唔對路就扭多啲或者扭少啲<br />\n同埋扭軚回軚都係可以早啲開始扭少少先<br />\n唔使去到彎位先一下扭盡佢"},{"pid":"259924ea689cf0391b7dc927bbe1e7a1303ee067","tid":109891,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"打得機多就知個彎要轉幾多，你學車車速慢，自己預判要扭幾多，多咗少咗咪再扭或者回<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4b088377af6f401058fd7c6f76e3b33a045d18","tid":109891,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:59:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你每次入彎都攞唔到最佳嘅路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />整係知車頭要出左少少先再轉<br />\n但有時扭得太少 師傅就話我偏離左條線<br />\n有時扭太多 就話我痴太埋條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77fff690c8c36bcfd7a089aee4c9dcb6b20df219","tid":109891,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:07:21.000Z","msg":"出左個亀頭先扭軚會清楚好多"},{"pid":"bf92ec8e9604e4d88213225b238e1695ab466e83","tid":109891,"uid":53663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:09:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出左個亀頭先扭軚會清楚好多</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec89844c09ddfccc02123a7296069d65f356d3d1","tid":109891,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:09:13.000Z","msg":"望住個車頭方向<br />\n扭到部車就黎直咪回軚"},{"pid":"0881eccb3e1a7878be601f4954acd18d6a5ef40b","tid":109891,"uid":48341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:24:15.000Z","msg":"唔好等到架車對正條路先回軚就唔會扭多"},{"pid":"bd49002b91f920a77ac34808c1a726a5dc05c4a6","tid":109891,"uid":31809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:31:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌，落機鋪玩兩轉灣岸頭D 先啦，呢啲嘢講感覺㗎嘛</blockquote><br />\n係咪認真有用先？<br />\n係嘅話我聽晚即刻去揸兩揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\